Plamena M
Varna, Bulgaria
8
Reviewed June 12, 2023
Best BBQ in Da Nang!
We were very impressed by this place because the staff was super friendly and the food was more than amazing. We didn't know what to try, so the staff quickly recommended some nice food to eat so we trusted them. We tried the shrimp, the pork belly, beef and oisters (can't say enough words about the green spicy sauce) . What made the experience even greater was that we cooked the food ourselves on a tiny BBQ next to our tables. The restaurant is very nice, the staff speaks English well and welcomes people from all around the world. Please stop by this place, you won't regret it!
