41
Reviewed July 12, 2022
Excellent experience, would not change anything
Once we arrived via grab, the owner prepared our seating and gave us a quick orientation of the menu.
He recognized that we are Singaporeans and did not hesitate to recommend us the common popular dishes, which we went ahead for.
Interesting BBQ service, food did not take long to come (but we were early)
Food was tasty, well marinated, and the bill was a lot smaller than we estimated!
Easy experience, tourist friendly but local prices.
Would recommend!
