copycaleb
Klang, Malaysia
135
Reviewed December 8, 2019
Interesting Dining Experience
What can I say? This place serves really good barbecued delicacies. Sure, it's hot, it's smoky, it's sweaty but it's well worth it. Come prepared to sweat and go home for a shower after. Their dishes are well-marinated with rich flavours and the mini charcoal barbecue grills are easy to handle. One of their specialties is cooked using hot stones in a pot. Make sure you order that. I would definitely go there again if I'm ever in Da Nang.
Date of visit: January 2019
